 Villagers harvest chrysanthemums in Futang Village of Changsha City, central China's Hunan Province, Nov. 26, 2021. In recent years, Futang Village in Hunan focused on developing chrysanthemum industry through cooperating with enterprises and cooperatives to boost income of villagers and rural revitalization. (Xinhua/Chen Zeguo)  Villagers harvest chrysanthemums in Futang Village of Changsha City, central China's Hunan Province, Nov. 26, 2021. In recent years, Futang Village in Hunan focused on developing chrysanthemum industry through cooperating with enterprises and cooperatives to boost income of villagers and rural revitalization. (Xinhua/Chen Zeguo)  Villagers harvest chrysanthemums in Futang Village of Changsha City, central China's Hunan Province, Nov. 26, 2021. In recent years, Futang Village in Hunan focused on developing chrysanthemum industry through cooperating with enterprises and cooperatives to boost income of villagers and rural revitalization. (Xinhua/Chen Zeguo)  Villagers harvest chrysanthemums in Futang Village of Changsha City, central China's Hunan Province, Nov. 26, 2021. In recent years, Futang Village in Hunan focused on developing chrysanthemum industry through cooperating with enterprises and cooperatives to boost income of villagers and rural revitalization. (Xinhua/Chen Zeguo)  Villagers harvest chrysanthemums in Futang Village of Changsha City, central China's Hunan Province, Nov. 26, 2021. In recent years, Futang Village in Hunan focused on developing chrysanthemum industry through cooperating with enterprises and cooperatives to boost income of villagers and rural revitalization. (Xinhua/Chen Zeguo)  Villagers harvest chrysanthemums in Futang Village of Changsha City, central China's Hunan Province, Nov. 26, 2021. In recent years, Futang Village in Hunan focused on developing chrysanthemum industry through cooperating with enterprises and cooperatives to boost income of villagers and rural revitalization. (Xinhua/Chen Zeguo)  Village